  "text": {
    "location": "Understage Corridor",
    "paragraphs": [
      "The stage lights flicker, then die. In the sudden darkness, you hear the unmistakable <em>creak</em> of floorboards—boards that haven't been walked in <strong>fifty years</strong>.",
      "<strong>DIRECTOR:</strong> \"You're late for your own disappearance.\"",
      "The voice comes from everywhere and nowhere. This is <span class=\"faction-preservationist\">The Understage</span>—the labyrinth beneath the theater where the <strong>Preservationists</strong> guard what <span class=\"faction-revisor\">The Revisors</span> would rewrite.",
      "Your pockets are empty. Your <strong>Script</strong> is blank. And somewhere in these dark corridors, your past is waiting."
    ]
  },
